                Advanced Educational Campus Security for Safe Learning Environments
            </h1>
            <p class="speakable-services" style="font-size:20px; line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:0; transition: all 0.3s ease; cursor: default;" 
               onmouseover="this.style.color='#152f45'; this.style.transform='scale(1.02)'; this.style.textShadow='0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)'" 
