                onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4b570'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#bf9e5b'">technology-enhanced security framework</strong> that blends a strong on-site presence with smart systems designed to protect students, staff, and facilities. In response to emerging safety concerns, we've scaled our campus security offerings to provide <strong style="color:#bf9e5b; transition: color 0.3s ease;" 
                onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4b570'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#bf9e5b'">flexible, rapid-deployment solutions</strong> that grow with your institution's unique needs and challenges. Our certified guards—both armed and unarmed—carry out regular <strong style="color:#bf9e5b; transition: color 0.3s ease;" 
                onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4b570'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#bf9e5b'">foot and vehicle patrols</strong>, upholding order and discouraging potential incidents before they arise. We supplement these patrols with advanced <strong style="color:#bf9e5b; transition: color 0.3s ease;" 
                onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4b570'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#bf9e5b'">biometric and mobile-credential access controls</strong>, ensuring that only approved individuals enter academic buildings, dormitories, and sensitive research facilities. Around-the-clock <strong style="color:#bf9e5b; transition: color 0.3s ease;" 
                onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4b570'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#bf9e5b'">video surveillance, perimeter alarms</strong>, and comprehensive risk evaluations underpin our proactive defense model. Every officer meets rigorous professional standards, and our <strong style="color:#bf9e5b; transition: color 0.3s ease;" 
                onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4b570'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#bf9e5b'">24/7 emergency response procedures</strong> are fully aligned with federal Clery Act requirements and state educational safety regulations. Regularly scheduled patrols, strategically illuminated common areas, and ongoing <strong style="color:#bf9e5b; transition: color 0.3s ease;" 
                onmouseover="this.style.color='#d4b570'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#bf9e5b'">crisis-management training</strong> help foster a secure, welcoming campus atmosphere—so students can learn and thrive without distraction while maintaining the open, academic environment essential to higher education.
            </p>
            <div class="speakable-contact" style="margin-top:20px; font-size:18px;">
                <strong>Call This Number:</strong> +1-714-716-7430 | 
                <strong>Email:</strong> info@shieldwisesecurity.com
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Campus Security Features Section -->
        <section id="features" class="campus-features-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2 class="section-title">Comprehensive Campus Security Solutions</h2>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Advanced security services designed specifically for educational environments</p>

                <div class="campus-grid">
                    <div class="campus-card">
                        <div class="campus-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i>
                        </div>
