                    </div>

                    <div class="campus-card">
                        <div class="campus-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="campus-title">Emergency Response</h3>
                        <p class="campus-description">Rapid crisis response protocols aligned with Clery Act requirements and coordinated with local law enforcement and emergency services.</p>
